Deal with Our Casino in New England

WE LIVE TO PLAY

Find us by our large signature overhangs outside of our casino and feel at ease when you step inside to sails, corals, and other nautical dcor. Our casino in Lincoln, RI, is open 24-hours a day and brimming with tables, slots, a VIP lounge, and other grand gambling opportunities. We are one of the largest gaming and entertainment venues in Rhode Island with over 162,000 square feet of gaming space. Let the betting begin.

The valet charge is $10 for weekends (starting Fridays at 9AM through the end of the operating day Sunday) and $5 on Wednesdays starting at 9AM through Friday at 9AM.
